/>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T12:01:07.000Z","msg":"這就是中國"},{"pid":"71eca9844c84f56a9610001e5f3a6151a9f3fff5","tid":963152,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T12:06:31.000Z","msg":"仲有紫光 萊蒙<br />\n我都廢事講<br />\n講到口臭<br />\n<br />\n我而家只係擔心接左兩支火棒嘅 &ldquo;奇卵辟邪&rdquo; 巴打"},{"pid":"1d7525a433c40f3ce704a3351ea3f3ba28ed2089","tid":963152,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a52fffbd4b541990ff7f089027a4b471632f5ea4","tid":963152,"uid":54337,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T11:40:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>第一次仆街：樓市</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n樓價下半年準備升多10%，又無人講？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/716191\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/716191</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T12:10:22.000Z","msg":"差估署：11月私宅售價指數連挫4個月<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181231/mobile/bkn-20181231100409693-1231_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20181231%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20181231100409693-1231_00842_001.html&d=aPukUiJMoaG1miLfv3%2FqyzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=dc423d20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181231/mobile/bkn-20181231100409693-1231_00842_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n香港住宅樓價繼續滑落。差餉物業估價署最新數據顯示，今年11月份，私人住宅售價指數報366.3點，按月大幅下跌3.5%，連挫4個月，累挫7.2%；為今年2月後最低。<br />\n<br />\n月內，中小型單位樓價跌幅較大。實用面積1,075方呎及以下中小型住宅的售價指數報369.1點，按月再跌約3.58%。而實用面積1,075方呎以上大型住宅單位售價指數報312.6點，按月下調約1.79%。<br />\n<br />\n今年首11個月私宅售價指數仍升3.86%，較2017年同期12.94%升幅，低9.08個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n另外，11月份租金指數報195.9點，按月跌約0.76%，連升9個月斷纜。而今年首11個月仍增長約4.48%，較2017年同期的升幅7.83%，低約3.35個百分點。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下？<br />\n愛康健，樓市升一成？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64695fc10c50fd5804bb8984c5b0835dfadb78b7","tid":963152,"uid":54337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T12:14:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/26/105401_14eef6f7a7e330ac4e6c0eff8e0a1f9f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F26%2F105401_14eef6f7a7e330ac4e6c0eff8e0a1f9f.png&h=edf18882&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/26/105723_77afeb3865237b7c3e58bbe4caaa2018.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F26%2F105723_77afeb3865237b7c3e58bbe4caaa2018.png&h=cef9d041&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n月照何年樹<br />\n花逢幾世人<br />\n人面不知何處去<br />\n桃花依舊笑春風<br />\n<br />\n廢柴垃圾騙子愛康健，昔日意氣風發。<br />\n唔知道而家係被人打死，定係瞓街邊呢？"},{"pid":"eda92fb91d6066fe1312d8c29f453a359dcc2258","tid":963152,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T12:15:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>鞭屍完畢。</strong></span>"},{"pid":"6d9076ddf31e4ffa68f49fe0ec8ade39aa379d55","tid":963152,"uid":40478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T12:19:54.000Z","msg":"其實條友睇到支那經濟好淡<br />\n但又睇好香港樓市<br />\n可能有精神分裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32b3569b48ca52aec718ac08fec5483463b77950","tid":963152,"uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T13:00:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓主aa9<br />\n<br />\n年尾無單開發神經<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82003c0e8452277a18b8dae62edefe149e0e53e0","tid":963152,"uid":54337,"like":0,"disli